---
title: Rich Pork Ragu with Ricotta Clouds
description: Set the table before you start cooking because this pork ragu will be ready to serve before you know it! Rich pork ragu and al dente rigatoni are topped with savoury clouds of ricotta and delicious Parmesan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sauce-ragu-copieux-au-porc-11162cb7.jpg
